data.description: Welcome home to Cozy Living in this 3 bedroom 1 bathroom RANCH just steps from downtown Crown Point. As you enter, you automatically feel the warm and inviting atmosphere and see the seamless flow throughout. The intimate layout provides the opportunity for lasting memories with loved ones, while the location allows you to be well placed to all the amenities NW Indiana has to offer. One of the OUTSTANDING features of this home is the size of the bedrooms and The Closet Space!!!! Don't miss the huge corner lot where you can picture yourself hosting unforgettable gatherings or designing a vibrant garden space. All Appliances Stay!! Act now to unlock your journey to creating your perfect living space in this Crown Point gem!
